00:31:44,155 --> 00:31:49,368
And they had to rebuild it
over about a month or so,

685
00:31:49,494 --> 00:31:51,997
but it was interesting
working on the same set.

686
00:31:52,122 --> 00:31:53,749
And we changed
the camera movements

687
00:31:53,874 --> 00:31:55,375
so that it was very static.

