750
00:34:37,954 --> 00:34:40,123
So in the original version of this shot,
of this scene,

751
00:34:40,248 --> 00:34:43,668
she was mad, arms crossed,
because Kirk had used her.

752
00:34:43,793 --> 00:34:47,338
There was actually a second green girl,
as well, later in the movie.

753
00:34:47,630 --> 00:34:49,215
- That was a very funny scene.
- Yeah.

754
00:34:49,340 --> 00:34:51,552
Where Kirk basically goes
and apologises to her.

755
00:34:51,677 --> 00:34:52,927
By the way,
we gotta put that on the DVD, as well.

756
00:34:53,052 --> 00:34:54,221
- That's a great scene.
- That has to be on the DVD.

757
00:34:54,346 --> 00:34:56,974
But actually,
I think a lot of that stuff went away

758
00:34:57,099 --> 00:34:59,476
because Matt Reeves
came to see the movie.

