00:55:15,442 --> 00:55:17,945
Well, first of all,
all this stuff here was done

1192
00:55:18,070 --> 00:55:20,030
at the parking lot at Dodger Stadium.

1193
00:55:20,155 --> 00:55:23,367
We built essentially a third of the drill,

1194
00:55:25,494 --> 00:55:30,706
