1211
00:56:24,385 --> 00:56:25,429
- That's right.
- That whole sequence happens,

1212
00:56:25,554 --> 00:56:26,929
you're like, "It wasn't even on the plane."

1213
00:56:27,054 --> 00:56:28,764
I think one of the things that
that movie taught us,

1214
00:56:28,891 --> 00:56:31,559
