1217
00:56:37,815 --> 00:56:39,568
And it just happens over and over
and over again,

1218
00:56:39,693 --> 00:56:42,153
so the audience never gets
a sense that it's gonna rest.

1219
00:56:42,278 --> 00:56:45,740
And I remember we were kind of talking
about the logistics of this,

